w positive velocity\nbias; however, this effect appears to depend on numerical resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 1999 16:28:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Sep 2000 10:29:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
